===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A representation of [[visible]] reality produced by [[drawing]], [[painting]], [[printing]], [[photography]], etc.
# A painting.
#: ''There was a '''picture''' hanging above the fireplace.''
# A photograph.
#: ''I took a '''picture''' of that church.''
# {{context|informal}} A [[motion picture]].
#: Casablanca ''is my all-time favorite '''picture'''.''
# {{context|dated|informal}} {{italbrac|"the pictures"}} [[Cinema]] (''as a form of entertainment'')
#: ''Let's go to the '''pictures'''.''

